description: This release adds JobStateTimeLimitActions setting to the Job Queue API. It allows you to configure an action Batch can take for a blocking job in front of the queue after the defined period of time. The new parameter applies for ECS, EKS, and FARGATE Job Queues.
Added exceptions to CreateTrail, DescribeTrails, and ListImportFailures APIs.
Add RDS Provisioned and Serverless Usage types
Update maintenance mode message to share upcoming end-of-support
Added DES_EDE3_CBC to the list of supported encryption algorithms for messages sent with an AS2 connector.
